sources.description:
Lockdown: 2025 - In the shadows of a highly contagious virus, a family seeks shelter in the safety of their own home during a nationwide LOCKDOWN, in which MARTIAL LAW is declared. With nowhere to go and danger approaching, the family is forced to confront the evil from within before it consumes them all.
2021.  Stars: Marcia Beverly, James Black, Louie Ski Carr
